window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Most PIs chase bad guys. Astrid Knightstorm chases demons.</b></p> <p>Just when Astrid Knightstorm is starting to believe things are going her way, a precious fae gemstone crumbles in her hands. Worse, it belongs to a High Priestess who hates her guts.</p> <p>As punishment, Astrid is ordered to investigate a disturbance in the treacherous fae Wildlands. What she finds is Vorathium, a demon literally hell bent on destruction.</p> <p>As creatures spill through the weakening barriers and a feral werewolf prowls Austin's streets, Astrid makes a shocking discovery. Her parents are alive, trapped in the Realm of Lost Souls.</p> <p>Now she's caught between fae dynasty politics and a demon who feeds on despair and wants nothing more than to escape to the mortal world.</p> <p>Some cases test your skills. This one could cost her family.</p> <p><b>Twisted Fae is book two in the electrifying Knightstorm Arcane Investigations urban fantasy series. Perfect for fans of Jim Butcher's Dresden Files, Patricia Briggs, and Ilona Andrews, this fast-paced adventure features a snarky wizard detective, supernatural mysteries, and a world where Magick hides in plain sight.</b></p>"; 
